<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>more info</title>
    <style>
        html {
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        body {
            background-color:#f1eee9;;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
        }

        section {
            padding: 80px;
        }

        .hero {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            width: 65%;
            margin: auto;
        }

        div {
            margin-right: 40px;
            padding-top: 0;
        }

        h1 {
            color: orange;
            font-size: 3em;
            padding-bottom: 25px;
        }

        p {
            color: black;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 70px;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .cta {
            color: white;
            background: #f9d678;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            border-radius: 50px;
        }

        .cta:hover {
            text-decoration: none;
            background: orange;
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 996px) {
            .hero {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
                justify-content: center;
                padding: 30px;
                padding: 10px;
                width: 85%;
            }

            .hero img {
                order: 1;
                margin-bottom: 40px;
            }

            .hero div {
                order: 2;
                height: auto;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                margin-right: 0;
            }

            .home p {
                padding: 0 50px 0 50px;
                margin-bottom: 50px;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 470px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.2em;
            }
        }
        .notification {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background-color: #ff4444;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        
    </style>
    <link rel="icon" href="https://i.ibb.co/nRKDFNv/Screenshot-2024-06-05-120657-removebg-preview.png">

</head>

<body>
    <div id="notification" class="notification">Action not allowed!</div>

    <section class="hero">
        <div>
            <h1>Over view about Dropshipping and AffiliateMarketing</h1>
            <p>Dropshipping is an e-commerce business model where the retailer does not keep goods in stock. Instead, when a customer makes a purchase, the retailer purchases the item from a third party (usually a wholesaler or manufacturer) who then ships the product directly to the customer.<br>
                How Dropshipping Works:<br>
               1. Setting Up an Online Store: The retailer sets up an online store and lists products for sale.<br>
                2.Customer Places an Order: A customer orders a product from the retailer's online store.<br>
                3.Forwarding the Order: The retailer forwards the order details to the dropshipping supplier.<br>
                4.Supplier Ships the Product: The supplier ships the product directly to the customer.<br>
                5.Profit Margin: The retailer earns a profit margin on the difference between the price they charge the customer and the price they pay the supplier.</p>
            <a class="cta" href="/Home">VIEW MORE</a>
        </div>
        <img src="home-banner-image.png" alt="">
    </section>
</body>
<script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', (event) => {
        const notification = document.getElementById('notification');
    
        function showNotification(message) {
            notification.textContent = message;
            notification.style.display = 'block';
            setTimeout(() => {
                notification.style.display = 'none';
            }, 2000);
        }
    
        // Disable right-click
        document.addEventListener('contextmenu', (event) => {
            event.preventDefault();
            showNotification('Right-click is disabled!');
        });
    
        // Disable copy
        document.addEventListener('copy', (event) => {
            event.preventDefault();
            showNotification('Copying is disabled!');
        });
    
        // Disable paste
        document.addEventListener('paste', (event) => {
            event.preventDefault();
            showNotification('Pasting is disabled!');
        });
    
        // Disable cut
        document.addEventListener('cut', (event) => {
            event.preventDefault();
            showNotification('Cutting is disabled!');
        });
    });
    
</script>
</html>